used with the \f[CR]balancesheet\f[R]/\f[CR]balancesheetequity\f[R]
commands
.IP \[bu] 2
\f[CR]\-\-cumulative\f[R] or \f[CR]\-\-historical\f[R] disables
\f[CR]\-\-row\-total/\-T\f[R]
